{"tid":950831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵受供電故障影響　部份來往西九及福田站班次取消","createTime":"2018-12-21T23:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T04:18:47.000Z","uid":36901,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bd28f936bd411beb796b1d7ff159f74c1537175c","tid":950831,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T23:02:21.000Z","msg":"【出門注意】高鐵受供電故障影響　部份來往西九及福田站班次取消<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受供電影響，部分高鐵列車取消。（港鐵網頁）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2018-12-22 05:39<br />\n<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-12-22 06:05<br />\n港鐵表示，由於受電力公司供電故障影響，部份來往香港西九龍站及福田的高速鐵路短途列車班次取消。請乘客留意。<br />\n<br />\n有關班次的詳資料，請留意於香港西九龍站發放的最新資訊，亦可致電高速鐵路購票及客務熱綫（852）2120 <a href=\"http://0888查詢或瀏覽高速鐵路網站www.mtr.com.hk/highspeed；如乘客若在購票時有留下聯絡電話，港鐵會再另行通知。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0888%E6%9F%A5%E8%A9%A2%E6%88%96%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD%E9%AB%98%E9%80%9F%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.mtr.com.hk%2Fhighspeed%EF%BC%9B%E5%A6%82%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E8%8B%A5%E5%9C%A8%E8%B3%BC%E7%A5%A8%E6%99%82%E6%9C%89%E7%95%99%E4%B8%8B%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%EF%BC%8C%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%9C%83%E5%86%8D%E5%8F%A6%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E3%80%82&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3e8168a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0888查詢或瀏覽高速鐵路網站www.mtr.com.hk/highspeed；如乘客若在購票時有留下聯絡電話，港鐵會再另行通知。</a><br />\n<br />\n以下班次將會取消（暫時截至下午約1時半為止）：<br />\nG5814, G5836, G5813, G5816, G5835, G5838, G5815, G5818, G5837, G5840, G5817, G5820, G5839, G5842, G5819, G5822, G5841, G5821"},{"pid":"d43e5375cca758ce48802a9fd0827df3ea20f56b","tid":950831,"uid":86375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"抵啦屌你老母!"},{"pid":"51b32c7835d3b03cc1770af238732698a145efe1","tid":950831,"uid":65406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:06:52.000Z","msg":"黨既恩情"},{"pid":"e07537e06cd01affcdceb5690087ab86dde3431a","tid":950831,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-